    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This driver\u2019s example boasts crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and a smooth-shifting 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis dynamics remain sharp, aided by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Maintenance is up to date with a comprehensive VANOS service and reinforced subframe mounting points\u2014critical for this",
