      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3, a quintessential driver's machine powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six. This example features a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, providing exceptional tactile feedback and power delivery. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a recently serviced Vanos unit to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Suspension bushings and dampers remain firm, maintaining the platform's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and turn-in precision. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including rod bearing clearances and throttle body synchronization\u2014are within spec, making this an ideal candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes visceral performance",
